OL,4,CGB News says presenter Guto Harri
OL,5,Cbreached standards by taking the knee
OL,6, GB News host Guto Harri is not expected
OL,7, to appear for the rest of the summer
OL,8, after the channel said he breached its
OL,9, standards by taking the knee on air in
OL,10, support of England footballers.
OL,12,FHarri was discussing the racist abuse
OL,13,Fagainst black players after England's
OL,14,Fdefeat in the Euro 2020 final.
OL,16,FBut his actions sparked a backlash and
OL,17,Fboycott threat from some viewers.
OL,19,FGB News said: "We let both sides of the
OL,20,Fargument down by oversimplifying a very
OL,21,Fcomplex issue."
